Why Package Exports Matter
Loading chain when using MessageStrip:
1. Load control wrapper (MessageStrip.js)
2. Wrapper depends on package export (@ui5/webcomponents.js)
3. Package export depends on base package (@ui5/webcomponents-base.js)
4. Base loads native bundle (MessageStrip.js)
Without package exports:
❌ UI5 loader error: Cannot find @ui5/webcomponents.js
❌ No way to declare base dependencies
❌ Wrong loading order breaks controls
With package exports:
✅ All modules resolve correctly
✅ Base packages load first
✅ Controls work as expected
